    public abstract class AbstractWebUiContextHandlerInterceptor<T extends WebUiContext>
extends org.springframework.web.servlet.handler.HandlerInterceptorAdapter
    Interceptor that constructs the WebUiContext corresponding to this particular request. Requires an AbstractWebUiContextRegistry to be present in the ApplicationContext.
